#, fuzzy
msgid "For example, set `Category` to `SocialMotivation`, and set `ApplicationCallbackDomain` to either `localhost` or the domain name provided by Ngrok, see the <<redirect_url>> for more information."
msgstr "例如，将 `Category` 设置为 `SocialMotivation` ，并将 `ApplicationCallbackDomain` 设置为 `localhost` 或 Ngrok 提供的域名，更多信息请参阅 <<redirect_url>> 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.8/guides/security-openid-connect-providers.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Strava does not enforce that the redirect (callback) URI which is provided as an authorization code flow parameter is equal to the URI registered in the Strava application because it only requires configuring `ApplicationCallbackDomain`. For example, if `ApplicationCallbackDomain` is set to `www.my-strava-example.com`, Strava will accept redirect URIs such as `www.my-strava-example.com/a`, `www.my-strava-example.com/path/a`, which is not recommended by OAuth2 best security practices, see link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/draft-ietf-oauth-security-topics#name-insufficient-redirect-uri-v[Insufficent redirect_uri validation] for more information.\n"
"Therefore you must configure a redirect path when working with the Strava provider and Quarkus will enforce that the current request path matches the configured `quarkus.oidc.authentication.redirect-path` value before completing the authotization code flow. See the <<exact_redirect_uri_match>> for more information."
msgstr "Strava 不会强制要求作为授权码流参数提供的重定向（回调）URI 等于在 Strava 应用程序中注册的 URI，因为它只需要配置 `ApplicationCallbackDomain` 。例如，如果将 `ApplicationCallbackDomain` 设置为 `www.my-strava-example.com` ，Strava 将接受 `www.my-strava-example.com/a` 、 `www.my-strava-example.com/path/a` 等重定向 URI，而这并不是 OAuth2 最佳安全实践所推荐的，更多信息请参阅 link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/draft-ietf-oauth-security-topics#name-insufficient-redirect-uri-v[Insufficent redirect_uri validation] 。因此，在使用 Strava 提供商时，您必须配置重定向路径，Quarkus 将强制执行当前请求路径与配置的 `quarkus.oidc.authentication.redirect-path` 值相匹配，然后再完成验证码流程。更多信息请参阅 <<exact_redirect_uri_match>> 。"

